	<td><span class="topic">Is Kickstarter always a good idea?</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=17511">http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=17511</a></span></td>
